title: Cart, from a processional group
description: dark grey; two-wheel cart attaches to donkey (L2006.128.1.1); roof of cart is a rectangle with slight upward flare at short ends; roof has a dome at center with a conical ribbed point; there is a black mount; mount: Lcube 2.5 MS
creditline: Lent by David and Flinnina Dewey
